query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '' OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.Phenotype is null
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, PerC.Phenotype OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and len(PerC.Phenotype) = 1 and PerC.Phenotype not like '%0%'

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, PerC.Phenotype OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and len(PerC.Phenotype) = 6 and PerC.Phenotype not like '%0%' and substring(cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)), 1, 2) != '11' and substring(cast(PerC.Phenotype as varchar(6)), 5, 2) != '11'
